    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-bg pt-32 pb-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">
                Our Mission: Connecting Australians with Trusted Allied Health Professionals
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-white/90">
                Building on a legacy of excellence to serve communities nationwide
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            
            <!-- Our Story -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Story</h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
                        FixMySpine began as a trusted name in North Sydney, where for years we served the local community as a reputable allied health clinic. Our practitioners built strong relationships with patients, earning a reputation for quality care, professionalism, and genuine commitment to helping people achieve better health outcomes.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
                        That legacy of trust wasn't something we wanted to keep confined to one suburb. We realised that Australians across the country deserve access to the same level of quality and transparency when searching for allied health professionals. Too often, people struggle to find reliable information about chiropractors, physiotherapists, osteopaths, and other practitioners in their area.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
                        So we evolved. FixMySpine transformed from a single clinic into something much bigger—a comprehensive, curated directory designed to connect Australians with verified, quality healthcare professionals throughout the nation. We've taken the trust and standards we built in North Sydney and expanded them to create a platform that serves the entire Australian community.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Mission -->
            <div class="mb-16 bg-secondary p-8 rounded-lg">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-text mb-4">
                    We're committed to making quality healthcare more accessible by:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-text"><strong>Providing transparency:</strong> Real patient reviews and detailed practitioner profiles help you make informed decisions about your healthcare.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-text"><strong>Ensuring quality:</strong> We carefully curate our directory, working only with licensed, professional practitioners who meet our standards.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-text"><strong>Supporting practitioners:</strong> We give quality healthcare providers the tools and visibility they need to grow their practices and help more patients.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-text"><strong>Building community:</strong> By connecting patients and practitioners across Australia, we're creating a healthier, more informed community.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- What We Offer -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">What We Offer</h2>
                
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">For Patients</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-text">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Comprehensive search by location and specialty</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Verified practitioner profiles with qualifications</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Authentic patient reviews and ratings</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Easy comparison of practitioners and services</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">For Practitioners</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-text">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Professional listing with detailed profile options</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Enhanced visibility through premium features</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Patient inquiry management tools</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Analytics to track profile performance</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Our Values -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Values</h2>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">Trust & Integrity</h3>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We maintain the highest standards of honesty and transparency in everything we do. Our reputation was built on trust, and we protect it fiercely.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">Quality Over Quantity</h3>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We carefully curate our directory to ensure every practitioner meets our professional standards. It's not about having the most listings—it's about having the right ones.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">Patient-Centered</h3>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            Your health and wellbeing come first. Every feature we build and decision we make is guided by what's best for patients seeking quality care.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">Australian Focus</h3>
                        <p class="text-text">
                            We understand the unique needs of Australian healthcare consumers and practitioners, and we're committed to serving our local communities with excellence.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <div class="bg-primary p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
