                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Company</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="/about" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">About Us</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/contact" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Contact</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/pricing" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Pricing</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">For Practitioners</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
